{"tid":725541,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"犯規整傷沙拿？　拉莫斯：我瞓得不知幾好 良心絕對沒有受到責備。","createTime":"2018-07-01T17:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T18:46:13.000Z","uid":54373,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eee2b9757a4282735b2f405f9db1d8e0d018a743","tid":725541,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T17:15:09.000Z","msg":"西班牙後衛沙治奧拉莫斯表示，他沒有因為被指在上月底歐聯決賽犯規、導致效力利物浦的埃及國腳穆罕默德沙拿受傷一事而失眠，強調自己的良心絕對沒有受到責備。<br />\n<br />\n該名西班牙國家隊隊長說：「我完全沒有為這事失眠，也未受良心的責備。」埃及足總周四已經證實，養傷多時的穆罕默德沙拿，百分之百可以在周五鬥烏拉圭的A組分組賽披甲。<br />\n<br />\n今次是埃及自從1990意大利世盃後，事隔28年再次亮相世盃決賽周。"},{"pid":"42920d863f34de72647b24b725f4fa6653804817","tid":725541,"uid":26232,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T17:16:14.000Z","msg":"終於可以搭飛機翻屋企繼續瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed72919b59cb2fea43ca79840889e712c09d3d9","tid":725541,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5c5df10f12f1cda664897f83b0ba9029062651","tid":725541,"uid":67146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T17:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7778e67bde438d848368eda00c1ce9f39de3c6e","tid":725541,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T18:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}